      },
      "date": "2013-09-24 11:11:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nHi Andreas,\n\nThanks to the help of Johann Lombardi and Niu Yawei, we've made some progress on this project. But as you can see, this work is not completed and needs more time to finish. We are currently working on the lfs command updates and hopefully the full patch will be ready for usage in one or too months.\n\nAnd ofcourse, any advice or code review is welcome. Thanks for the help!",
