      "message": "Patch Set 12:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/597a0906-317f-11e3-bce4-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
