        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2013-11-08 10:07:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 13: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(32 inline comments)\n\nSome high-level improvements are needed for this patch:\n- documentation in the lustre-manual.  Please file an LUDOC ticket to track the manual updates (if not already done)\n- documentation in the man page\n- there need to be a bunch of test cases added to this patch\n- is it now possible to add MDTs to a pool?  That would be very useful for DNE, and could probably be added in a separate patch\n- I'm surprised at the number of changes in the MGC code to handle this.  I'd think most of the pool handling could be re-used?\n- the tests need to be fixed so they will work against older servers",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 13
    },
